pendulum and swing back the other way. And there

04:10.844 --> 04:15.170
would be money coming. I've seen these 
oscillations within the

04:15.190 --> 04:26.125
federal staff before, and I thought it would occur 
again. But Skip wasn't interested in that. And

04:26.866 --> 04:31.292
with his background, I didn't understand that. So 
although it still exists on paper, And we still do a

04:36.089 --> 04:40.334
