08:13.220 --> 08:26.774
had very limited viewpoints, very limited 
outlook and outreach. And of course, as the

08:26.794 --> 08:30.777
research program was started by Mr. Rudder and Mr. 
Parson, it flowered. And of course, that outreach

08:33.700 --> 08:37.985
effort expanded. And our worldly awareness, if 
