08:43.578 --> 08:59.011
realization that every great

08:43.578 --> 08:59.011
news, again, if you look at MIT and Stanford and 
Telecom, what makes them great? Well, as we've

08:59.031 --> 09:10.761
already said, it's not their

08:59.031 --> 09:10.761
academic programs.

09:10.781 --> 09:12.702
It's part of the old graduate programs, but 
certainly not undergraduate programs. And

09:12.722 --> 09:13.483
research programs, yeah. But more than that, they 
apply their expertise to

09:13.835 --> 09:37.260
solve problems that are sort of like the old RAIN 
program, problems that are associated with

09:13.835 --> 09:37.260
national

09:13.835 --> 09:37.260
needs.

09:40.447 --> 09:52.459
