little bundle of cash. Well, maybe not such a

12:31.952 --> 12:32.693
little bundle. And we

12:33.922 --> 12:51.664
ought to go by people, people that have clout, 
people that have international expertise. And it

12:51.684 --> 12:52.845
doesn't take many. You need some sort of critical 
mass. I mean, one guy's not going to make it, but

12:57.611 --> 12:58.892
three or four, yeah. Again, if they were working in 
complementary areas, you couldn't have a guy here

12:58.912 --> 13:01.035
and another guy there. To some extent, I'm here 
walking teeth. and uh well in any event that was the

