17:02.524 --> 17:16.800
syndrome, and what that means is that a 
philosophical

17:17.270 --> 17:33.427
viewpoint which looks at the Soviets as mirror 
images of us, that fundamentally they're just

17:17.270 --> 17:33.427
like us. They think like us. They want the same 
things in the world as we do. They respond to

17:39.113 --> 17:40.915
pressures in the world as we do. Of course, that's 
